@startuml
title P01-DEMO Ticket Flow [Ref: REQ-001, REQ-002, BR-001]

|Staff|
start
:Create ticket;
:Set title, description, priority, requester email;

|System|
:Validate required fields and email format;
if (Valid?) then (yes)
  :Save ticket as To Do;
else (no)
  :Show validation message;
  stop
endif

|Staff|
:Move ticket to In Progress;
:Add review notes;
:Move ticket to Review / Test;

|PM / QA|
if (Review notes complete?) then (yes)
  :Move ticket to Done;
else (no)
  :Return to In Progress;
endif

stop
@enduml
